    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan<br /><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Koyumi Clan, Level 8+<br />Through tradition, the techniques passed down from generations have reached further heights. You gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li>Increase your Strength, Dexterity, or Wisdom score by 1, to a maximum of 20</li><li>When you would cast a Koyumi Clan Hijutsu the range is increased by 30 feet and Koyumi Clan Hijutsu with an area of effect has its area of effect increased by 10 feet.</li><li>Increase the damage die of Koyumi Clan Hijutsu by +1 when you would cast a jutsu with an attack roll or saving throw.</li><li>When you would upcast a Koyumi Clan Hijutsu you decrease the upcast cost by -1.</li></ul>",
